OL,4,G1055FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe competition kicks off at the
OL,6,     GBrighton Surf Hotel, where Jeremy
OL,7,     GMann and his Russian wife Elena
OL,8,     Ghope that their hands-off hosting
OL,9,     Gstyle will win the day, despite
OL,10,     Gthe lack of breakfast.
OL,11,G1125FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GActor and antiques dealer Robert
OL,13,     GGray hosts at Number 16, in
OL,14,     GGreenwich, London. He charms his
OL,15,     Gguests with his hosting, but Jan
OL,16,     Gand Les find the dusty decor off-
OL,17,     Gputting.
